trans-unit.source: Represents the <see langword="<ReferenceList>" /> element used in XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta l'elemento <see langword="<ReferenceList>" /> utilizzato nella crittografia XML.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Questa classe non può essere ereditata.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> class represents the `<ReferenceList>` element of an encrypted document XML signature defined by the XML encryption specification.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> classe rappresenta il `<ReferenceList>` elemento del documento crittografato della firma XML definita dalla specifica la crittografia XML.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> class contains references to <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elements that were encrypted by a key contained within another <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> element.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> classe contiene riferimenti a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> e <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> gli elementi che sono stati crittografati mediante la chiave contenuta all'interno di altra <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elemento.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> class uses <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> elements to reference <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> elements, and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> elements to reference <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elements.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> utilizzato dalla classe <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> elementi facciano riferimento <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> elementi, e <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> elementi facciano riferimento <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elementi.

trans-unit.source: You can add only <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> or <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> objects to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> collection.
trans-unit.target: È possibile aggiungere solo <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> o <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> oggetti per il <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> insieme.

trans-unit.source: For more information about XML encryption standards, see http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core.
trans-unit.target: Per ulteriori informazioni sugli standard di crittografia XML, vedere http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core.
